org.nasdanika.html.model.app.util

Interface ActionProvider

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, BiFunction<BiConsumer<EObject,Action>,ProgressMonitor,Action>, Diagnosable, ExecutionParticipant, ExecutionParticipantInfo, Function<BiConsumer<EObject,Action>,Action>

    public interface ActionProvider
extends Function<BiConsumer<EObject,Action>,Action>
    Adapter interface. Takes a map of semantic elements to their default actions and creates an action for the target. Implementations shall call the argument BiConsumer passing the target and resulting action as argument to use later in resolve() phase.
    Author:
    Pavel
